      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FEDERAL BLONDE (8) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at Capalaba behind Needs Time (20.87) in a Mix 5. Chased the leaders and with a clean run can be prominent. Expected to feature in the finish again. OXLEY CHARM (6) settled down midfield and held her position to the line when finishing 4th (30.41) at this track. Solid record here at the distance winning five races. Speedy beginner who can find the front despite the tricky draw. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. SUPER SEAFARER (1) comes off an average run last start when sixth at Q Lakeside over 457m behind Daytona Sunset (26.28) in a Grade 5. One of the better hopes. CYCLONE RANGER (2) should be thereabouts despite an unplaced run here most recently.",
